            <span>&middot;</span>
            <span>Specialist in PE/PA firm principal K-1 partnership distribution, AECOM/Jacobs/Stantec publicly listed W-2 + RSU, licensed PE/RA staff W-2 + bonus, solo Schedule C with E&amp;O deductions, and favorable non-SSTB QBI treatment for architect &amp; engineer mortgages</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hero-image">
